  "texts": [
    "Consider a task-specific module C, parameterized by ζ, which embodies a downstream task:",
    "Here, oi represents the output of our task.",
    "Our training objective aims to minimize the loss function L, which quantifies the discrepancy between oi and the target label yi, thereby indicating whether oi correctly represents the label for xi:",
    "This approach allows the fine-tuning process to concentrate explicitly on the representation and comprehension of labels, while simultaneously harnessing the intrinsic knowledge embedded within Θ.",
    "The adjustment of parameters Φ and ζ empowers the model to further refine its ability to map textual inputs to their corresponding labels."
